{
  "name": "post_legal_hold_policy_assignments",
  "description": "Assign a legal hold to a file, file version, folder, or user.",
  "parameters": {
    "type": "object",
    "properties": {
      "body": {
        "properties": {
          "assign_to": {
            "description": "The item to assign the policy to",
            "properties": {
              "id": {
                "description": "The ID of item to assign the policy to",
                "example": "6564564",
                "type": "string"
              },
              "type": {
                "description": "The type of item to assign the policy to",
                "enum": [
                  "file",
                  "file_version",
                  "folder",
                  "user"
                ],
                "example": "folder",
                "type": "string"
              }
            },
            "required": [
              "type",
              "id"
            ],
            "type": "object"
          },
          "policy_id": {
            "description": "The ID of the policy to assign.",
            "example": "123244",
            "type": "string"
          }
        },
        "required": [
          "policy_id",
          "assign_to"
        ],
        "type": "object"
      }
    }
  },
  "handler": "http",
  "request": {
    "method": "POST",
    "url": {
      "$uri": "https://api.box.com/2.0/legal_hold_policy_assignments"
    },
    "body": {
      "$": "body",
      "encode": "json"
    }
  },
  "responses": {
    "201": {
      "$encode": "markdown",
      "$block": [
        {
          "$h1": "Legal hold policy assignment (Base)"
        },
        "Legal Hold Assignments are used to assign Legal Hold\nPolicies to Users, Folders, Files, or File Versions.\n\nCreating a Legal Hold Assignment puts a hold\non the File-Versions that belong to the Assignment's\n'apply-to' entity.",
        "**Key properties:**",
        {
          "$ul": [
            "**id**: The unique identifier for this legal hold assignment",
            "**type**: `legal_hold_policy_assignment`",
            "**assigned_at**: When the legal hold policy assignment object was",
            "**assigned_by**",
            "**assigned_to**",
            "**deleted_at**: When the assignment release request was sent.",
            "**legal_hold_policy**"
          ]
        },
        {
          "$lang": "json",
          "$code": {
            "$encode": "json",
            "$indent": true,
            "$content": {
              "$": "$.body"
            }
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    "default": {
      "$encode": "markdown",
      "$block": [
        {
          "$h1": "Client error"
        },
        "A generic error",
        "**Key properties:**",
        {
          "$ul": [
            "**code**: A Box-specific error code",
            [
              "**context_info**: A free-form object that contains additional context",
              {
                "$ul": [
                  "**message**: More details on the error."
                ]
              }
            ],
            "**help_url**: A URL that links to more information about why this error occurred.",
            "**message**: A short message describing the error.",
            "**request_id**: A unique identifier for this response, which can be used",
            "**status**: The HTTP status of the response.",
            "**type**: `error`"
          ]
        },
        {
          "$lang": "json",
          "$code": {
            "$encode": "json",
            "$indent": true,
            "$content": {
              "$": "$.body"
            }
          }
        }
      ]
    }
  }
}
